---
import '../styles/od-tokens.css';
---

<section class="testimonials">
  <div class="testimonials__inner">
    <blockquote class="testimonials__quote">
      <p class="testimonials__text">
        "AI应该放大你的能力，而不是替代你的判断。在这场变革中，找到属于你的"人机协同节奏"，才是真正的护城河。"
      </p>
      <footer class="testimonials__footer">
        <cite class="testimonials__author">壹目贯维</cite>
      </footer>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    background-color: var(--od-color-bg-testimonials);
    padding: var(--od-space-layout);
  }

  .testimonials__inner {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .testimonials__quote {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .testimonials__text {
    font-family: var(--od-font-body);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--od-color-text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--od-space-layout);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .testimonials__footer {
    margin-top: var(--od-space-layout);
  }

  .testimonials__author {
    font-family: var(--od-font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--od-color-text-secondary);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .testimonials__author::before {
    content: "— ";
  }
</style>
